# ===== Built data =====
# The Chroma index is rebuilt automatically on first boot from descriptions.json,
# so it stays out of git. The corpus metadata, thumbnails, AND the video files
# are tracked so the private repo deploys a fully playable site.
data/chroma/

# Keep the committed sample corpus + its thumbnails:
!data/sample/
!data/sample/**
